[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pony rides: Off-road in a wheelchair

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Simon Mulholland and his pony, Obama, offer wheelchair users a chance to go off-road across terrain that would otherwise be impossible for them to access.

